# API Routes

All external AI/TTS calls **only** in `src/app/api/`.

## Pattern

```
POST /api/scenario/advance  → load node spec → Claude SSE → structured JSON chunks
POST /api/scenario/judge    → user input → risk_flag → next node_id
POST /api/tts/stream        → sentence → Typecast stream → audio chunks
```

## Security

- Read keys from `process.env` — never expose to client
- Validate input with Zod before LLM call
- Inject `forbidden_content` into system prompt per node
- Post-filter response for blocked patterns

## Response

- Use SSE (`ReadableStream`) for LLM text streaming
- Return structured JSON — never raw LLM free text to client
- STT: accept text from client (Web Speech API); do not store audio

## Error Handling

- Graceful fallback: text-only if TTS fails
- Teen routes: reject TTS requests entirely
